Package: hmr
Version: 1.1-0
Title: High-performance Hadoop Map/Reduce R interface based on iotools
Author: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>, Taylor Arnold <taylor.arnold@acm.org>
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Depends: R (>= 2.9.0)
Imports: iotools (>= 0.3-0)
Suggests: RSclient, rjson, krb5
Description: High-performance Hadoop Map/Reduce R interface based on
iotools. Enables R users to create and submit Hadoop map/reduce jobs
with a single function and provides an intuitive interface to write
distributed code in R.
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
URL: http://www.rforge.net/hmr
